title: VIDEO: Michelle Grattan on Bill Shorten
text:
University of Canberra Vice-Chancellor Stephen Parker and Michelle Grattan discuss the week in politics including Bill Shorten’s second anniversary as opposition leader, his chances at the next election, the possibility of a Labor frontbench reshuffle and the safety of his leadership.
Video Bill Shorten The Week in Politics You might also like 1 day to go: on the eve of the election, a string of UKIP gaffes could be making Farage sweat. Nigel Roddis/EPA Election 2015
